  Kou2-cha2 kou2-cha2, ti7 Chiu-tiau5 u7 3 e5 long5-hu; chit8 e5 si7 siN3 “Ong5”, chit8 e5 si7 siN3 “Tan5”, koh chit8 e5 si7 siN3 “Ng5” e5. SaN e5 lang5 long2 siuN7 khoaN3 u7 siaN2 pan7-hoat thang tit-tioh8 chhan5-hng5 khah choe7 a2 boe7; in-ui7 na7 beh eng7 chiN5 boe2, tioh8 su-iau3 chin-choe7 chiN5, sou2-i2 ....... 
  U7 chit8 jit8, siN3 Ong5--e5 khi3 mng7 hit chng e5 hu3-ong Kong2, “Hu3-ong ah! U7 sim2-mih8 pan7-hoat thang tit-tioh8 chhan5-hng5 khah choe7 mah?” 
  Hu3-ong chin giam5-siok ka7 i in3 kong2, “Ong5 sang3! Li2 tak8 jit8 khi3 hng5-nih, than3 chhau2 iau2-be7 hoat e5 si5, tioh8 kin2 khau chhau2.” 
  Ong5 sang3 eng7 ki5-koai3 e5 bin7 ka7 i kong2, “Chong2-si7, Hu3-ong ah! Chhau2 to iau2-be7 hoat chhut-lai5, thai3 oe7 thang khau i.” 
  Hu3-ong chi2-u7 in3 i kong2, “Chiau3 goa2 sou2 ka7 li2 kong2 e5, khi3 choe3 khoaN3 bai7!” 
  Ong5 sang3 boe7 liau2-kai2 Hu3-ong sou2 ka7 i kong2 e5 oe7, m7-ku2 tak8 jit8 chiau3 Hu3-ong sou2 kong2 e5, tui3 cha2-cha2 chiu7 khi3 hng5-nih, kau3 e5-hng te7 it liap8 chhiN chhut; bak8-chiu thi2 chhin-chhiuN7 phiat-a2 hiah toa7, tit8-tit8 chhe7 chhau2; na7 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 ki chhau2 iN2-a2 puh chhut-lai5, i chiu7 kiaN chit8-e7! Ia7 kong2, “Ah! Hai7 lah! Hu3-ong kong2, than3 chhau2 iau2-be7 hoat tioh8 kin2 khau chhau2.......” I chiu7 na2 kong2 na2 khau hiah e5 chhau2 iN2-a2, khau kau3 moa2-sin tang7 koaN7. 
  Tan5 sang3 ia7 khi3 chheng2-mng7 Hu3-ong, “KhoaN3 u7 pan7-hoat thang tit-tioh8 chhan5-hng5 khah choe7 a2 bo5?” 
  Hu3-ong chiau3 ka7 Ong5 sang3 kong2 e5 oe7 ka7 i kong2, “Than3 chhau2 iau2-be7 hoat e5 si5, tioh8 kin2 khau chhau2.” 
  Tan5 sang3 soa3 ai3 chhio3 kong2, “Chhau2 to boe7 hoat, thai2 oe7 thang khau i?” 
  Hu3-ong koh kong2, “Chiau3 goa2 sou2 kong2 e5 khi3 choe3 bai7!” 
  Tan5 sang3 khiok u7 chiau3 Hu3-ong sou2 kong2, tak8 jit8 khi3 hng5-nih khoaN3-khoaN3, m7-ku2 khah siong5 che7 tiam3 chhiu7-kha teh tuh-ka-che7. Bo5 ku2 chhau2 hoat khi2-lai5 lah! Hoat kau3 2, 3 chhun3 lah! Tan5 sang3 khoaN3, chit8 phian3 hng5 hoat kau3 long2 si7 chhau2, chiah kong2, “Oah! Hai7 lah! Bo5 khau chhau2 boe7 eng7-tit lah!” Tan5 sang3 chiah khai-si2 piaN3-mia7 khau chhau2, khau kau3 moa2-sin moa2-bin7 long2 si7 koaN7. Chong2-si7 cheng5 khau, au7 hoat, iu7 jit8-thau5 iam7 pha3-pha3, koh chhau2-kun teng3 chin an5, khau kau3 beh bo5 mia7. 
  SiN3 Ng5 e5, ia7 khi3 chheng2-kau3 Hu3-ong, khoaN3 u7 ho2 pan7-hoat thang tit-tioh8 chhan5-hng5 khah choe7 a2 bo5? Hu3-ong ia7 si7 an2-ni ka7 i kong2, “Than3 hng5-nih e5 chhau2 iau2-be7 hoat e5 si5 tioh8 kin2 khau chhau2.” 
  Na7-si7 siN3 Ng5 e5 ai3 chhio3. I han2-tit khi3 hng5-nih, na7 khi3, sui-jian5 khoaN3 chhau2 hoat ia7 long2 bo5 khau, pang3 hng5 choe3 chhau2-pou, chi2-u7 toa3 chhu3-nih hoan-lok8, khun3 tiong-tau3. Chng-nih e5 lang5 long2 phoe-pheng5, “Ng5 sang3 e5 hng5; m7-si7 tiu7-a2-hng5, si7 chhau2-a2-hng5.” 
  Bo5 joa7 ku2 siu-koah e5 si5 kau3 lah! Ong5 sang3 e5 siu 10 pe7; Tan5 sang3 e5 siu 2 pe7; Ng5 sang3 e5 siu 10 hun7 chi it. 
  Chng-nih e5 gin2-na2 liam7 choe3 koa-khek lai5 chhiuN3, “Ong5 sang3 e5 hng5 10 pe7 siu-seng5; Tan5 sang3 e5 hng5 2 pe7 siu-seng5; Ng5 sang3 e5 hng5 chi2-u7 chap8 hun7 chi it siu-seng5.” 
  Choe3 pe7-bu2 e5 thiaN an2-ni ia7 chhiuN3 chit8 tiau5 koa hou7 in e5 kiaN2-ji5 thiaN: 
  “Tioh8 oh8 chhin-chhiuN7 Ong5 a-peh e5 chhan5-hng5; <BR>  Than3 chhau2 iau2-be7 puh, i chiu7 kin2 khau-tu5. <BR>  Ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7, sou2 u7 e5 phaiN2-tai7. <BR>  Than3 i iau2-be7 puh, tioh8 kin2-kin2 san-tu5. <BR>  Koh tioh8 ai3 phah-piaN3, ti7 lan2 e5 kang-tiaN5. <BR>  Chu2 chiu7 toa7 chiok-hok, hou7 lan2 tit khoai3-lok8.” 
  Lau7-pe7 kong2 chit e5 kou3-su7 hou7 in e5 kiaN2-ji5 thiaN. Sou2-i2 in e5 kiaN2 mng7, Ong5 a-peh au7-lai5 u7 piN3 ho2-giah8 mah? 
  Lau7-bu2 in3, Si7! In-ui7 i e5 chin7-lat8, chiu7 ni5-ni5 toa7 hoat-tat8, kau3 10 ni5 au7, i chiaN5-choe3 chit8 e5 toa7 hu3-ong. 
  （Lu2-soan Geh8-khan Te7 38 ki5, 1963 ni5 2 geh8) 
